dcterms:description: A publicly available dataset consisting of histological routine colon cancer nuclei patches, containing 22444 nuclei patches belonging to four classes: 'Epithelial', 'Inflammatory', 'Fibroblast', and 'Miscellaneous'. Each patch has a dimension of 32 × 32 × 3.
